[Installed X window system]
sudo yum groupinstall "X Window System" "Desktop" "Desktop Platform" "General Purpose Desktop"
init 5
(Note: X works on tty1 in the case of CentOS6)

[Installed Chromium]
cd /etc/yum.repos.d
wget http://people.centos.org/hughesjr/chromium/6/chromium-el6.repo
sudo yum install chromium
